WEBVTT

00:01.550 --> 00:05.200
For this little panda to be happy, the tree has to be happy.

00:06.200 --> 00:09.650
And for the tree to be happy, the air it breathes has to be happy.

00:10.650 --> 00:13.450
And if the air is happy, the climate is happy.

00:14.750 --> 00:17.550
And if the climate is happy, nature is happy.

00:20.550 --> 00:23.800
And if nature is happy, people and the way they live and work,...

00:24.000 --> 00:26.050
...and the panda are all happy.

00:26.900 --> 00:29.000
A happy future is a serious business.

00:29.350 --> 00:34.000
We work in partnership with governments, corporations, and communities to secure that future,...

00:34.400 --> 00:35.850
...because we're all connected.

00:36.200 --> 00:38.150
And that's WWF's business.

